# 🚀 First Year CSE AIML Roadmap 2026–2027  
**Very Simple English • Complete Beginner Friendly • Long & Detailed Guide**  
**For First-Year B.Tech CSE / AIML / AI & DS Students in India**

Hello!  
You are in **first year B.Tech CSE / AIML** (or similar branch) in India.  
Your goal = become a good **AI / Machine Learning Engineer** or **Data Scientist** in future.  
This roadmap is **very simple**, **step by step**, **long & detailed** so you understand everything clearly.  
No big words, no pressure. Just small daily steps.  

Most first-year students waste time on reels, only college syllabus, or jumping everywhere.  
**You will not.**  
Small daily work → big results in 2–3 years → good internships → high salary job (10–30+ LPA possible).

